Current Version: 1.0
Overview
Our group members are developing an online grocery delivery website to provide ease for the customers to get their groceries online and enhance the customer base of a super store.
Milestones
List of technological choices for front-end, back-end and databases Technical_Details_2 
Complete website with working features
Presentation to defend project in front of professor
Test the website at project defense
Complete login/signup page
Complete add to cart feature (Will be done by Berhan )
Complete feature where employees will label products as out of stock or in stock
Complete feature where delivery team can message each other if an item is missing from the order
Complete feature where it tells the customer when the order has been delivered to their house
Complete feature where customer can refund an order
Complete feature where customers can message customer support 
Complete a properly working website with a database 
Deliverables
